Agent Performance Metrics: Quality Assurance scores, Agent Satisfaction scores, Productivity metrics per agent, and Time to Proficiency for new hires. These indicate how agent assist is affecting agent experience and capability.

Business Impact Metrics: Revenue impact (from cross-sell/upsell recommendations), Compliance violation reduction, Attrition reduction, and Overall ROI. These connect agent assist to bottom-line business results.

Track these metrics continuously, establish baselines before implementation, and review them regularly with stakeholders. Organizations that maintain disciplined measurement practices realize 2-3 times greater ROI from their agent assist investments.

